if (50 & 1) {
  console.log('odd')
} else {
  console.log('even');
}

&
- Returns 1 if both are 1

|
- returns 1 if either is 1
- if both are 1, returns 1 too

^
- returns 1 if one is 1 and the other 0

~
- changes 1 to 0 and 0 to 1

Two's complement
- flips all the bits, then adds 1 to the end

<<
- moves to the left
- multiply by 2, shift << 1
- multiply by 4, shift << 2
- multiply by 3, shift << 1 then add 1
